'''Epsilon Composite''' is a French company created in 1987 by Stephane LULL, its current [[CEO]].
Turnover in 2012 was 21M€ with 190 employees.<ref>Frédéric Parisot, [http://www.usinenouvelle.com/article/epsilon-composite-inaugure-une-nouvelle-usine-en-gironde.N182475 Epsilon Composite inaugure une nouvelle usine en Gironde], L'Usine Nouvelle, September 21st 2012</ref>

Epsilon Composite produces a wide range of [[Carbon-fiber-reinforced polymer]] (CFRP) products for various applications:<ref>Colette Goinère, [http://www.usinenouvelle.com/article/epsilon-composite-veut-repondre-aux-marches-de-l-aeronautique.N141114 Epsilon Composite veut répondre aux marchés de l’aéronautique], L'Usine nouvelle, November 4th 2010.</ref><ref>Airbus s'intéresse à Epsilon, Air et Cosmos n°2213, April 9th 2010, p.21</ref><ref>Claude Mandraut, [http://www.latribune.fr/entreprises-finance/tpe-pme/414745/epsilon-composite-diversifie-les-applications-de-la-fibre-de-carbone.html Epsilon Composite diversifie les applications de la fibre de carbone], La Tribune, may 14th 2010</ref>
* [[Manufacturing]] and printing machines ([[flexography]] and [[textile]] industries)
* Energy ([[oil]] & [[Natural gas|gas]] offshore exploitation, [[wind turbine]]s)
* [[Civil Engineering]]
* Camera support equipments ([[tripods]])
* [[Automotive]] and leisure applications
* [[Aerospace]]<ref>Frédéric Parisot, [http://www.usinenouvelle.com/article/epsilon-composite-inaugure-une-nouvelle-usine-en-gironde.N182475 Epsilon Composite inaugure une nouvelle usine en Gironde], L'Usine Nouvelle, September 21st 2012</ref><ref>[http://www.aerorecherchecorac.com/ CORAC website]</ref>

The main production process used by the company is [[pultrusion]].

Epsilon Composite is mainly dealing with international customers (90% of the turnover comes from exports), mostly from [[Japan]] and [[Germany]]. The production site is located in Gaillan, [[France]]

